snippet.title: The Ward Official Trailer by John Carpenter & Amber Heard
snippet.description:
John Carpenter's current reputation as a spent force is undeserved, even if he's not made much recently that knocked anyone's socks off. This one is more a step in the right direction than a fully fledged return to form. Amber Heard plays a young amnesiac in a psychiatric institution trying to figure out why a ghostly apparition/zombie thing is brutally killing her fellow patients. Unfortunately, the audience is way ahead of her -- we've seen this many times before.


Release Date: 08 Jul 2011
Genre: Horror
Language: English


Cast : Amber Heard, Danielle Panabaker, Lyndsy Fonseca, Mamie Gummer, Mika Boorem


Director:   John Carpenter
Producer:   Peter Block,  Doug Mankoff
Music Director:   Mark Kilian


http://calacitra.com
